From 2803b2d55385006acf45ddceb0b330cd187c69c5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Yang Chao <iyeatse@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 7 Jun 2026 15:17:49 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] features(objc): fix conflicting Swift name for
 LightGlueMatcher.create

LightGlueMatcher derives from DescriptorMatcher and adds a static factory
create(const String& modelPath, ...). The Objective-C bindings generator
emits its 1-argument form as the selector create:, which clashes with the
inherited DescriptorMatcher::create(MatcherType) selector (also create:)
that carries a different swift_name, so clang refuses to build the opencv2
Objective-C module:

  LightGlueMatcher.h: error: 'swift_name' and 'swift_name' attributes are
  not compatible

This collision exists only in the Objective-C bindings, so fix it there
instead of in the public header (which would also rename the Python and
Java bindings). Add a func_arg_fix entry in
modules/features/misc/objc/gen_dict.json renaming the Objective-C selector
to createFromFile, mirroring how DescriptorMatcher::create and
BFMatcher::create are disambiguated. The Swift name stays create(modelPath:)
and the C++/Python/Java APIs are unchanged.

Fixes #29256
---
 modules/features/misc/objc/gen_dict.json | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/modules/features/misc/objc/gen_dict.json b/modules/features/misc/objc/gen_dict.json
index e88518de2d5b..fd9f7bdaaffc 100644
--- a/modules/features/misc/objc/gen_dict.json
+++ b/modules/features/misc/objc/gen_dict.json
@@ -17,6 +17,9 @@
         "DescriptorMatcher": {
             "(DescriptorMatcher*)create:(NSString*)descriptorMatcherType" : { "create" : {"name" : "create2"} }
         },
+        "LightGlueMatcher": {
+            "(LightGlueMatcher*)create:(NSString*)modelPath scoreThreshold:(float)scoreThreshold backend:(int)backend target:(int)target" : { "create" : {"name" : "createFromFile"} }
+        },
         "FlannBasedMatcher": {
             "FlannBasedMatcher": { "indexParams" : {"defval" : "cv::makePtr<cv::flann::KDTreeIndexParams>()"}, "searchParams" : {"defval" : "cv::makePtr<cv::flann::SearchParams>()"} }
         },
